item.title: Andalucia
item.description: The Mystical Music of Andalucia, recorded in 2002 and published in 2004, features four solo works for piano and seven of Barbara Solís’s arrangements for viola and piano. Copies of the manuscript scores of Ms. Solís’s arrangements heard on this recording are available on this website (see Musical arrangements by Barbara Solís).
